  "content": "<blockquote data-pid=\"5CYkC3eW\">译者： <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/31cf1b829bffdcf9f8bed9bafa37d2ff\" data-hash=\"31cf1b829bffdcf9f8bed9bafa37d2ff\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$31cf1b829bffdcf9f8bed9bafa37d2ff\">@荆慢慢2.1</a> </blockquote><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/434074509\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3fc5e91c7a88c26207775c8301afbe1f_720w.jpg\" data-entity-type=\"article\" data-entity-data=\"null\" class=\"internal\">如何写出好卡片：利用间隔重复创造理解</a><p data-pid=\"ANl5flzu\">离上面这篇文章发布，也过去了一个多月，收到了不少读者的来信，其中 <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/142b134f84b13c4c5005c686b949b03a\" data-hash=\"142b134f84b13c4c5005c686b949b03a\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$142b134f84b13c4c5005c686b949b03a\">@咖喱羊</a> 提出了一个很有启发的问题：「精准性」和「一致性」到底有什么区别？</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-eefd619ebe54af8223aa1bd3056bd8a8_1440w.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"628\" data-rawheight=\"479\" data-original-token=\"v2-eefd619ebe54af8223aa1bd3056bd8a8\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"628\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-eefd619ebe54af8223aa1bd3056bd8a8_r.jpg\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"sR1K-tpk\">这个问题在我们汉化组里引起了大讨论，各方观点你来我往，乱成了一锅粥。最后我们决定给原文作者 Andy 发一封邮件，向他请教。他的回复，我们翻译如下：</p><hr/><p data-pid=\"7FeVfZxi\">你好，Jianjie，感谢你发来的疑问，我恐怕没能选择很好的词语去描述他们，有一些读者也提出了相似的问题。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><ul><li data-pid=\"hs4Qwj1u\">「精准性」是关于避免模糊的答案；<br/><br/></li><li data-pid=\"ZC_7E-hv\">「一致性」是指保证问题每次诱导的答案是<b>一样</b>的<br/><br/></li></ul><p data-pid=\"yv12bw2P\">举例：</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><ul><li data-pid=\"tw4mgoZh\">精准不一致：<b>制作西式蛋饼的第一步是什么？</b><br/><br/></li><ul><li data-pid=\"GhZIfVIp\">（这个回答并不含糊，但它会根据你想要做的蛋饼样式而颇有不同）<br/><br/></li></ul><li data-pid=\"EshwJNhq\">不精准但一致：<b>什么是有机物（organism）？</b><br/><br/></li><ul><li data-pid=\"aFJBTJg5\">（你的答案每次都是相似的，但它其实可能很模糊，提取了个寂寞）<br/><br/></li></ul></ul><p data-pid=\"NsDiNQaR\">希望对你有帮助，新年快乐！</p><hr/><p data-pid=\"2epAZsDP\">原信如下：</p><blockquote data-pid=\"UGLUxE23\">Reply：「Precision」 vs 「Consistent 」：what&#39;s the distinction in between ?<br/>Hi there, Jianjie. Thanks for this kind note. I’m afraid that my choice of words here may be flawed. Several other readers have asked similar questions.<br/>Precision is about avoiding vague answers.<br/>Consistency is about making sure the question elicits the same answer each time.<br/>Precise but inconsistent: what’s the first step to making an omelette?<br/>(the answer won’t be vague, but it will vary a great deal depending on the style you imagine creating)<br/>Imprecise but consistent: what is an organism?<br/>(you’ll probably give a roughly similar answer each time, but it’ll probably be pretty vague) <br/>I hope that helps. Happy new year!</blockquote><hr/><p data-pid=\"2TXDKOvD\">感谢 Andy 的回复，希望能够解答读者们的疑惑！</p><hr/><p data-pid=\"kZwjm4VC\">更多有关制卡原则的内容，请关注：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/collection/614280525\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">制卡原则与知识表述</a><p></p>",
